yanwittmann.api

Class GoogleTranslate

  • java.lang.Object
    • yanwittmann.api.GoogleTranslate

  • public class GoogleTranslate
extends java.lang.Object
    Use an object of this class to translate a text using the Google Translate API.
    Use bulk requests to speed up the translation process and to prevent error 429 (you can only perform a certain amount of requests in a time window).
    This class has been written by Yan Wittmann.
    Author:
    Yan Wittmann
